articles.title: PM Modi Live Updates: PM Modi, Albanese rename Sydney suburb as ‘Little India’ at mega event in Australia - The Indian Express
articles.description: PM Modi in Australia Live Updates: Speaking at the event, PM Narendra Modi announced that India will open a new consulate in Brisbane soon.
articles.content:
Tens of thousands of overseas Indians are expected to cheer Prime Minister Narendra Modi at a rally in Sydney's biggest sporting arena today, a rare mass showing for a foreign leader in Australia.
